== To all Network Report Recipients in #{@organization.country_name}:

%p
  %strong Application status: In review
%p
  == A comment regarding #{@organization.name}'s application to the UN Global Compact has been posted.
%table{:border => 1, :cellspacing => 1, :cellpadding => 15, :style => 'background: #E5EDF8;'}
  %tr
    %td
      %strong Latest Comment to applicant:
      = simple_format(@organization.comments.first.body)

%p If you would like to assist the organization with submitting the above requested information, please find the contact information below:

%p
  %strong== Profile for #{@organization.name}:

- @row_style = 'text-align: right; padding-right: 10px'

%table
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Letter of Commitment:
    %td= link_to @organization.commitment_letter_file_name, 'http://unglobalcompact.org' + @organization.commitment_letter.url
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Type:
    %td= @organization.organization_type_name
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Sector:
    %td= @organization.sector_name
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Employees:
    %td= @organization.employees
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Website:
    %td= @organization.url

%p
  %strong CEO / Highest Level Executive Information
%p
  %table
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Name:
      %td= @ceo.full_name_with_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Title:
      %td= @ceo.job_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Address:
      %td
        ==#{@ceo.address} #{@ceo.address_more}
        %br/
        ==#{@ceo.city} #{@ceo.state} #{@ceo.postal_code}
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Phone:
      %td= @ceo.phone
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Email:
      %td= @ceo.email

%p
  %strong Login information:

%p
  You may login as this contact here:
  = link_to @contact.full_name_with_title, sign_in_as_admin_contact_url(@contact.id, tab: 'sign_in_as_contact_point')

%p
  %strong Contact Point Information
%p
  %table
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Name:
      %td= @contact.full_name_with_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Title:
      %td= @contact.job_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Address:
      %td
        ==#{@contact.address} #{@contact.address_more}
        %br/
        ==#{@contact.city} #{@contact.state} #{@contact.postal_code}
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Phone:
      %td= @contact.phone
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Email:
      %td= @contact.email

- if @organization.participant_manager
  %p== Please feel free to contact #{@organization.participant_manager_name} at #{mail_to @organization.participant_manager_email} in case you have further questions.

%p Sincerely,

%p The Global Compact Office

United Nations Global Compact
